---
title: Grilled Greek Turkey with Bulgur Salad
description: Greek pesto and zesty Lemon-Pepper Seasoning make a bold and flavourful marinade for tender turkey. Want even more flavour? Marinate in the morning and refrigerate until you're ready to grill! A classic chopped salad of cucumber, tomato, grilled red onion and briny feta make a special summer side
